originalText.text: I first came to Ascenza after a snowboarding injury last year. In my first visit, I could tell that John was very knowledgeable and he was able to diagnose and explain the anatomy behind the pain I was experiencing. Over the next year, John helped me rehabilitate my shoulder and while I was nervous about snowboarding again this season, I was able to regain my confidence enjoy snowboarding again now that my shoulder has healed up. I love working with the amazing therapists at Ascenza and have now transitioned to doing personal training with John. I will be recommending Ascenza to all of my family and friends!

originalText.text: Brandon Hulasiya has been my PT for more than 3 years! I have an arthritic left knee and also foot problems, such as an old metatarsal injury. After treatment by Brandon, I went for knee x-rays, as my surgeon wants me to do a knee replacement. He was disappointed that there was "no change" in my knee--and I credit Brandon with that! No surgery needed, and I am able to go up and down subway stairs carrying my 25-pound rolling book bag! Brandon actually listens when you explain how your problem feels! He is the best PT anyone could want! He rates more than 5 stars.

originalText.text: Ascenza has been a lifesaver for me and my shoulder recovery. I'm so lucky to have PTs that really put thought into my care and don't just follow a boiler plate routine. Every visit I feel like my latest progress and issues are considered and implemented into our exercises and I know it's one of the main reasons I'm already back to playing sports.

originalText.text: I've been to other PT facilities and Ascenza is by far superior. They are small and personalized, which is refreshing since most are corporate owned and make you feel like a number. Dorothy is so knowledgable, patient and easy to work with. I recommend Ascenza highly.

originalText.text: I have been a client of Brandon Hulasiya since he was based in a different location, and I gladly followed him to this new practice. The level of care that I receive at Asenza is incomparable. All the exercises feel very personal to my physical therapy needs. I have also observed the other staff at Ascenza; they are all friendly and professional.  They are all extremely attentive to their client's needs. I do not hesitate to recommend Ascenza to anyone seeking a Physical Therapy or Training practice.
